# upstream-diff CLI writes per-block reports next to each block's
# upstream-state.json. The reports are transient build artifacts —
# regenerated on every run, including in CI — so they should never
# enter the working tree's diff. The 10 already-tracked report files
# predate this rule and stay tracked until a dedicated cleanup PR
# removes them.
resources/js/visual-editor/blocks/**/upstream-diff-report.json
